## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of how political ideologies influence policymaking. Additionally, the focus was primarily on the United States, which may not reflect the influence of political ideologies in other political systems. Further research could include a broader range of countries and political contexts to provide a more comprehensive understanding.

